Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.12,0:00:22.98,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.333\fad(700,700)}魔法の言葉 覚えている 虹の始まったところ
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.32,0:00:30.34,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.333\fad(700,700)}あの時世界の全てに 一瞬で色が付い
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.80,0:00:37.72,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.333\fad(700,700)}本当の声はいつだって 正しい道を照らしている
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.94,0:00:45.32,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.333\fad(700,700)}なんだって疑っているから とても強く信じている
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.52,0:00:52.70,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.333\fad(700,700)}心臓が動いている事の 吸って吐いてが続く事の
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.88,0:00:59.74,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.333\fad(700,700)}心がずっと熱い事の 確かな理由を
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.02,0:01:06.92,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.333\fad(700,700)}雲の向こうの銀河のように どっかで無くした切符のように
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.10,0:01:14.48,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.333\fad(700,700)}生まれる前の歴史のように 君が持っているから
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.94,0:01:20.84,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.333\fad(700,700)}それだけ わかっている
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.22,0:01:28.50,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.333\fad(700,700)}僕だけ わかっている
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.12,0:00:22.98,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.333\fad(700,700)}记得魔法的话语 彩虹开始的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.32,0:00:30.34,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.333\fad(700,700)}那时世界的一切 瞬间带上了色彩
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.80,0:00:37.72,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.333\fad(700,700)}真正的声音无论何时 都在指引正确的道路
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.94,0:00:45.32,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.333\fad(700,700)}无论何事都要怀疑 所以才坚定的相信
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.52,0:00:52.70,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.333\fad(700,700)}心脏在搏动 呼吸在持续
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.88,0:00:59.74,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.333\fad(700,700)}内心总是如此炽热的 确切的理由
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.02,0:01:06.92,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.333\fad(700,700)}如同云之彼端的银河 如同丢失在某处的车票
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.10,0:01:14.48,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.333\fad(700,700)}如同降生前的历史 由你持有
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.94,0:01:20.84,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.333\fad(700,700)}只有此事 很清楚
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.22,0:01:28.50,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.333\fad(700,700)}只有我 很清楚
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.40,0:23:10.14,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(400,400)}その声は流れ星のように
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.40,0:23:15.70,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(400,400)}次々に耳に 飛び込んでは光って
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.92,0:23:19.78,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(400,400)}魚のように集まりだして
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.00,0:23:24.32,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(400,400)}冷たかった胸に 陽だまりが出来た
Dialogue: 0,0:23:24.94,0:23:29.00,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(400,400)}普通の触れ方を知らないから
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.24,0:23:33.98,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(400,400)}戸惑っていたら 触れてくれた手に
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.32,0:23:38.58,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(400,400)}どれだけ夜をくぐり抜けても
Dialogue: 0,0:23:38.80,0:23:44.12,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(400,400)}ずっと冷めないままの熱が 脈を打つ
Dialogue: 0,0:23:44.48,0:23:48.08,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(400,400)}君がいるそれだけで
Dialogue: 0,0:23:48.46,0:23:54.04,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(400,400)}命の全部が輝く
Dialogue: 0,0:23:54.18,0:23:57.60,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(400,400)}凍りついた心に
Dialogue: 0,0:23:57.72,0:24:03.98,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(400,400)}その鼓動が響き火を灯す
Dialogue: 0,0:24:04.40,0:24:08.74,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(400,400)}いくつもなくなったあとに
Dialogue: 0,0:24:09.12,0:24:13.56,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(400,400)}強く残った ひとつ残った
Dialogue: 0,0:24:13.96,0:24:18.32,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(400,400)}離れない いつでも側に
Dialogue: 0,0:24:18.52,0:24:26.36,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(400,400)}僕の中に 一番近くに
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.40,0:23:10.14,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(400,400)}那个声音像流星一般
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.40,0:23:15.70,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(400,400)}接二连三的跃入耳里 熠熠生辉
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.92,0:23:19.78,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(400,400)}像鱼一样开始聚集
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.00,0:23:24.32,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(400,400)}冰冷的胸间有了阳光的暖意
Dialogue: 0,0:23:24.94,0:23:29.00,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(400,400)}因为不知道普通的接触方式
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.24,0:23:33.98,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(400,400)}所以迷惘 对于碰触我的那只手
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.32,0:23:38.58,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(400,400)}无论穿越多少黑夜
Dialogue: 0,0:23:38.80,0:23:44.12,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(400,400)}一直不曾冷却的热量 在鼓动着
Dialogue: 0,0:23:44.48,0:23:48.08,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(400,400)}只因为有你存在
Dialogue: 0,0:23:48.46,0:23:54.04,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(400,400)}生命的一切都绽放光辉
Dialogue: 0,0:23:54.18,0:23:57.60,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(400,400)}在冰冻的心间
Dialogue: 0,0:23:57.72,0:24:03.98,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(400,400)}那份鼓动回响着 点燃火焰
Dialogue: 0,0:24:04.40,0:24:08.74,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(400,400)}失去太多太多之后
Dialogue: 0,0:24:09.12,0:24:13.56,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(400,400)}顽强的留下 唯一留下
Dialogue: 0,0:24:13.96,0:24:18.32,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(400,400)}不会分离 无论何时都在身边
Dialogue: 0,0:24:18.52,0:24:26.36,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(400,400)}在我心里 最为接近的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.63,0:01:43.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&H5C5C5C\3c&Hffffff\pos(192,294)}受赠之物①
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.76,0:02:05.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,12月
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.22,0:02:07.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,圣诞节将至的时候
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.76,0:02:10.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,香子姐再次给我打来电话
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.93,0:02:13.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,忘拿的东西？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.39,0:02:14.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,手表？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.07,0:02:23.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 找到了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.68,0:02:49.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.47,0:02:52.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,后藤才刚送我的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.18,0:02:54.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没戴着的话他会生气的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.23,0:03:00.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是的 说不定感冒了 都怪你
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.11,0:03:03.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以才让你在车站前的麦当劳等着
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.44,0:03:05.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,才不要 在那种嘈杂的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.28,0:03:08.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么去你家不行呐
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.62,0:03:11.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.21,0:03:20.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,让我猜猜你刚才在想什么吧 零
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.30,0:03:26.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,开玩笑啦 表情这么恐怖
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.55,0:03:34.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,呐 年末有什么打算
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.47,0:03:36.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,会回来吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.14,0:03:40.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不 年底还有相当多的对局
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.77,0:03:42.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,得好好学习才行
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.31,0:03:43.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对局？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.73,0:03:48.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你今年的对局就剩24号和安井先生的排位战了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.45,0:03:51.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哦对了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.78,0:03:55.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,说起安井先生 他似乎终于决定要离婚了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.04,0:03:58.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,平时佝偻着腰 性格懦弱
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.87,0:04:01.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,输棋后却酗酒大闹还赌博
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.42,0:04:03.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真亏他妻子能忍到现在
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.84,0:04:06.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,最可怜的还是他女儿吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.46,0:04:08.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一定很害怕吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.17,0:04:11.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,和一旦输棋就像变了个人似的爸爸
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.89,0:04:13.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,生活在同一个屋檐下
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.43,0:04:16.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 真讨厌
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.35,0:04:20.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是他女儿说
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.98,0:04:23.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,希望至少到圣诞节都能和爸爸在一起
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.44,0:04:25.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,无法忍受的厌恶
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.19,0:04:26.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这样的…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.19,0:04:30.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是感人呢 你不觉得吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.07,0:04:33.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,姐姐这纠缠不休让人恼火的口吻
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.53,0:04:36.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,呐 零 你在听吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.24,0:04:38.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,更重要的是
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.08,0:04:39.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.29,0:04:42.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就连这种充满恶意的言语
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.84,0:04:49.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,围巾要被吹飞了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.97,0:04:51.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要围的话就围好嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.09,0:04:54.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也想听下去的自己
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.22,0:04:57.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小孩子还真是可怜呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.77,0:05:01.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为没法选择自己的父母
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.27,0:05:07.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哦 不过是呢 你不同呐
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.77,0:05:09.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你自己选择了父母呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.74,0:05:13.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,选了别人家的父亲
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.04,0:05:20.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,呐 爸爸 可以打开了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.50,0:05:22.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 可以
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.09,0:05:29.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等等 这大熊算什么嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.42,0:05:33.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,爸爸你真是的 我已经是中学生了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.26,0:05:35.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哇 是Game Bomb
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.68,0:05:42.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果是这个家庭的孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.31,0:05:46.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是以棋手为目标的话
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.06,0:05:50.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那美丽的棋子所蕴含的价值 意义
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.69,0:05:53.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,和父亲必中的想法
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.78,0:05:55.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不可能不明白的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.53,0:05:58.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么样 零
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.03,0:06:01.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你会不会觉得玩具比较好
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.16,0:06:05.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不 非常感谢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.71,0:06:07.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我非常开心
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.50,0:06:10.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不可能不明白
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.51,0:06:16.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,姐姐 弟弟 当时感到了多大的伤痛
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.06,0:06:23.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,呐 真是令人难过呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.18,0:06:27.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,赢了棋回家的爸爸和输了棋回家的爸爸
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.44,0:06:32.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,作为最后的圣诞节的回忆
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.28,0:06:34.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,到底哪一个比较合适呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.78,0:06:40.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,除了体育和音乐以外都还凑合吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.16,0:06:43.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,话说回来 你数学和物理超好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.91,0:06:46.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就是这样 给
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.00,0:06:49.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,九点三十分前要到千驮谷吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.46,0:06:50.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,得抓紧了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.71,0:06:54.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不过你还真忙啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.38,0:06:56.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就连结业式都要对局
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.80,0:07:00.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,虽说出席天数勉强够了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.39,0:07:02.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但第三学期再增加对局数的话
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.60,0:07:03.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,说不定会很危险呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.47,0:07:05.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小心哦 嘿嘿
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.02,0:07:06.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你是要我输吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.27,0:07:09.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不 这个 事关我的生计
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.13,0:07:19.30,Note,,0,0,0,,{\c&H353535&}{\an7\3c&HFFFFFF&}1-B\N圣诞派对\N田中家车库\N17：00-\N饮料500日元\N交换礼物1000日元
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.40,0:07:12.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,话说今天结业式完了之后
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.48,0:07:15.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们班的同学似乎打算开圣诞派对哦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.07,0:07:16.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你知道吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.28,0:07:19.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,诶…当然没听说过
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.53,0:07:20.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,请不要告诉我啦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.66,0:07:26.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,事已至此也没办法了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.83,0:07:29.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你啊 对局完了之后要不要回学校一趟
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.23,0:07:32.77,Note,,0,0,0,,{\fn@华康少女文字W5\frz-90\pos(1136,14)}可恶——\N我也没被邀请！！\N为什么！？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.67,0:07:32.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们两个邋遢地吃着蛋糕下将棋也行…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.06,0:07:32.77,Note,,0,0,0,,{\pos(310,498)}答案→因为是老师
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.63,0:07:34.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,突然消失
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.59,0:07:36.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,回头的时候已经不见了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.17,0:07:37.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,呀！等等嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.09,0:07:40.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这样一来我不就成了坏心眼的老师吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.09,0:07:41.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Oh No！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.14,0:07:43.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,至少听人家把话说完嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.85,0:07:45.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,呐 桐山
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.73,0:07:53.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,从什么时候开始的呢…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.69,0:07:57.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,开始觉得圣诞节很痛苦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.11,0:08:00.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,某个时刻突然这么觉得
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.78,0:08:03.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,像成绩单一样
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.37,0:08:05.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那一整年的…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.41,0:08:08.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这一年来
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.08,0:08:12.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我被朋友 家人 父母
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.46,0:08:14.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,多么深地爱着呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.05,0:08:18.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是以怎样的方式被爱着呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.94,0:08:32.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,安井六段
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.04,0:08:38.59,Top,,0,0,0,,车门要关了 请注意
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.66,0:08:43.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是他女儿说
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.41,0:08:47.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,希望至少到圣诞节都能和爸爸在一起
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.00,0:08:51.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,至少到圣诞节…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.88,0:09:05.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,赢了棋回家的爸爸
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.76,0:09:07.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,和输了棋回家的爸爸
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.68,0:09:12.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,作为最后的圣诞节的回忆
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.39,0:09:13.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,到底哪一个比较合适呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.19,0:09:16.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.94,0:09:18.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,零
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.46,0:09:36.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,到时间了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.71,0:09:42.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,请多指教
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.75,0:12:22.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我输了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.74,0:12:32.95,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&H5C5C5C\3c&Hffffff\pos(192,294)}受赠之物②
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.49,0:12:51.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我明白的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.99,0:12:53.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,总而言之 你是想说
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.45,0:12:55.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,「我中途就投降了」是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.45,0:13:00.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,和安井先生的对局
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.46,0:13:02.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在傍晚之前就轻松地结束了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.25,0:13:06.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,从8六步开始就让人不快
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.71,0:13:08.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在9五下桂
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.09,0:13:12.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,的确是这样
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.76,0:13:14.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果发现的话肯定是会这样下吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.60,0:13:18.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是呐 就是没发现
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.43,0:13:19.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没有办法
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.56,0:13:23.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你的话说不定知道
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.02,0:13:25.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可我就是不知道啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.48,0:13:26.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这也是没办法的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.19,0:13:32.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在仿若自言自语般的安井先生的叹息中
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.41,0:13:35.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,混杂着些许的酒气
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.32,0:13:37.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,让我心中烦闷不已
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.58,0:13:45.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,序盘在矢仓战法中安静缓慢地开始
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.50,0:13:50.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,慎重地 慎重地
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.09,0:13:53.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他谨慎的下法中仿佛有警告自己的声音
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.88,0:13:57.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别失误 别失误
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.94,0:14:10.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可是
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.44,0:14:13.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,午餐休息后不久
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.40,0:14:15.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,安井先生出现了失误
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.58,0:14:28.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只是短短的瞬间
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.21,0:14:30.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,安井先生也注意到了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.21,0:14:35.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不 如果之后从8六步开始
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.18,0:14:37.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,攻击玉头的话 结果也说不定
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.76,0:14:42.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果抽出马 盯紧了 胜败如何还未分
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.73,0:14:44.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就在这时
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.27,0:14:48.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,安井先生的轮廓却失去了力量
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.23,0:14:49.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,渐渐瘫软了下来
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.61,0:14:51.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.78,0:14:54.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明明…明明出路还没有完全消失
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.78,0:14:58.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,听说她女儿这么说过
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.45,0:15:00.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等等 为什么
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.74,0:15:01.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.04,0:15:03.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就这么简单地
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.62,0:15:04.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还不能松手
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.87,0:15:06.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,集中 意识
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.00,0:15:08.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,至少到圣诞节前
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.25,0:15:10.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,重要的东西
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.54,0:15:11.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就这样简单地…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.88,0:15:13.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,想和爸爸在一起
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.88,0:15:16.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎样都好 拜托了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.67,0:15:18.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要就这样松手
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.02,0:16:13.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我输了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.07,0:16:26.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,感想战到这样子就差不多了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.88,0:16:35.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,今天就点到为止 放过我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.80,0:17:23.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,安井先生 安井先生
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.51,0:17:25.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不在
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.68,0:17:26.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,去哪了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.85,0:17:29.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,找到了 安井先生
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.89,0:17:31.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他要去哪
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.48,0:17:33.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那边明明不是去车站
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.70,0:17:44.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,安井先生
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.49,0:17:48.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个 给
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.38,0:18:00.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不是我的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.34,0:18:01.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没见过
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.22,0:18:06.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,安井先生
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.89,0:18:08.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我知道的 你好烦啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.98,0:18:14.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明明是最后的圣诞节
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.10,0:20:58.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那全都是我的错吗！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.56,0:21:01.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那我到底要怎么做才好啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.77,0:21:04.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别开玩笑了！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.65,0:21:07.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明明就是弱者的错啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.07,0:21:09.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为弱小才会输啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.74,0:21:11.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,去好好学习啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.49,0:21:14.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我知道你没有这样努力啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.12,0:21:17.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,说什么我都知道但是做不到！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.45,0:21:18.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那就放弃啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.75,0:21:20.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,滚啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.16,0:21:23.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这边可是赌上一切的啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.88,0:21:26.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,除此之外我一无所有！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.63,0:21:28.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只剩将棋了啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.88,0:21:31.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要喝酒逃避啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.55,0:21:34.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,弱者就是一无是处啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.79,0:22:07.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果逃避的话…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.75,0:22:11.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果真的能逃避的话…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.67,0:22:14.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.14,0:22:23.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一边说着没有战斗的理由
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.73,0:22:25.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,事实上
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.85,0:22:29.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我深知自己的身体里栖息着野兽
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.32,0:22:33.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,即便是咬碎周身一切
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.20,0:22:36.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也会为了活下去而奔走的野兽
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.91,0:22:40.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,战斗一旦开始 那无论如何…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.99,0:22:44.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,都会把手伸向生存之路
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.58,0:22:47.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,即便要让某人不幸
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.96,0:22:51.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,无论怎样的世界在等我…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.41,0:23:00.91,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&H5C5C5C\3c&Hffffff\pos(1092,704)}受赠之物②
Dialogue: 0,0:24:33.52,0:24:36.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哇 是小零家呐
Dialogue: 0,0:24:36.61,0:24:38.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,来吧 小零 脖子伸长点
Dialogue: 0,0:24:39.70,0:24:41.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,零 是零吗
Dialogue: 0,0:24:41.82,0:24:42.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你没事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:24:43.16,0:24:44.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我真是个笨蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:24:44.95,0:24:47.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不是哦 是我希望你来…
Dialogue: 0,0:24:48.50,0:24:50.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,被帮助的人是我呐
Dialogue: 0,0:24:51.67,0:24:52.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,三月的狮子
Dialogue: 0,0:24:52.63,0:24:53.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,下集也请期诗哦
Dialogue: 0,0:24:54.13,0:24:57.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大家要多多关注我和桐山的活跃表现哦
Dialogue: 0,0:24:57.34,0:24:58.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,老师
